_of_the_Netherlands>Part of the [[Kingdom of the Netherlands]], but not of the [[European Union|EU]].</ref>\n*{{flag|New Caledonia}} \u2013 ''see: [[#CFP|CFP franc]]''\n*{{flag|New Zealand}} \u2013 [[Reserve Bank of New Zealand]] (''Te P\u016btea Matua'')\n*{{flag|Nicaragua}} \u2013 [[Central Bank of Nicaragua]] (''Banco Central de Nicaragua'')\n*{{flag|Niger}} \u2013 ''see: [[#UEMOA|West African Economic and Monetary Union]]''\n*{{flag|Nigeria}} \u2013 [[Central Bank of Nigeria]]\n*{{flag|North Macedonia}} \u2013 [[National Bank of the Republic of North Macedonia]] (''\u041d\u0430\u0440\u043e\u0434\u043d\u0430 \u0431\u0430\u043d\u043a\u0430 \u043d\u0430 \u0420\u0435\u043f\u0443\u0431\u043b\u0438\u043a\u0430 \u0421\u0435\u0432\u0435\u0440\u043d\u0430 \u041c\u0430\u043a\u0435\u0434\u043e\u043d\u0438\u0458\u0430'')\n*{{flag|Norway}} \u2013 [[Norges Bank]]\n\n=== O ===\n*{{flag|Oman}} \u2013 [[Central Bank of Oman]] (''\u0627\u0644\u0628\u0646\u0643 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0631\u0643\u0632\u064a \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0645\u0627\u0646\u064a'')\n*<span id=\"OECS\"></span>[[Organisation of Eastern Caribbean States]] \u2013 [[Eastern Caribbean Central Bank]]<ref>Although the [[British Virgin Islands]] are members of the [[Organisation of Eastern Caribbean States]], they do not use the [[Eastern Caribbean dollar]] as a [[de facto currency]].</ref>\n**{{flag|Anguilla}}\n**{{flag|Antigua and Barbuda}}\n**{{flag|Dominica}}\n**{{flag|Grenada}}\n**{{flag|Montserrat}}\n**{{flag|Saint Kitts and Nevis}}\n**{{flag|Saint Lucia}}\n**{{flag|Saint Vincent and the Grenadines}}\n\n=== P ===\n*{{flag|Pakistan}} \u2013 [[State Bank of Pakistan]] (\u0628\u06cc\u0646\u06a9 \u062f\u0648\u0644\u062a \u067e\u0627\u06a9\u0633\u062a\u0627\u0646)\n*{{flag|Palestine}} \u2013 [[Palestine Monetary Authority]] (\u0633\u0644\u0637\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0642\u062f \u0627\u0644\u0641\u0644\u0633\u0637\u064a\u0646\u064a\u0629)\n*{{flag|Panama}}  \u2013 [[National Bank of Panama]] (''Banco Nacional de Panam\u